description:
C&B tutorial on Ukraine: What's Putin's plan? Washington doesn't care about our border, but will spend millions on Ukraine's border. Neil Young tells Spotify to choose between Joe Rogan and his music catalogue. Crazy Fauciites inexplicably ratchet up on masks in school. Rice University swim coach speaks out against NCAA handling of Penn trans swimmer. C&B take some calls.
